            <div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-field-description field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__item"><p>The Minto Recreation Complex - Barrhaven was recently listed by Chatelaine Magazine as one of the <strong>top 10 best indoor pools in Canada</strong>! Read the <a href="https://www.chatelaine.com/living/best-indoor-pools-canada/#gallery/best-indoor-pools-in-canada/3">Best Indoor Pools in Canada article</a>.</p>
<p>The Minto Recreation Complex - Barrhaven&nbsp;includes a six lane, 25&nbsp;metre&nbsp;lap pool with three&nbsp;metre&nbsp;and one&nbsp;metre&nbsp;diving boards, and an access ramp (Pool Rentals, please contact&nbsp;<a href="mailto:mrcb@ottawa.ca">mrcb@ottawa.ca</a>). Two&nbsp;NHL sized ice rinks (one rink is accessible), with accessible change rooms (please contact City Wide Allocations&nbsp;<a href="mailto:sports@ottawa.ca">sports@ottawa.ca</a>&nbsp;for ice rentals).</p>
<p>Outside find an artificial turf sports field designed to meet&nbsp;CFL&nbsp;and FIFA design standards (please contact City Wide Allocations <a href="mailto:sports@ottawa.ca">sports@ottawa.ca</a>&nbsp;for field rentals).</p>
<p>Artwork suspended from the ceiling named&nbsp;Mr.&nbsp;Kurokawa.&nbsp;</p>
<p>Minto,&nbsp;an active sponsor of community initiatives, is proud to be associated with the City of Ottawa's Community Champions Program.</p>
</div>
      

